description: This test logs in, adds products, validates details, modifies the cart, and completes checkout.

steps.name: Navigate to the SauceDemo login page
Apply price filter and add two products to the cart
Validate product details in the cart for Sauce Labs Onesie and Sauce Labs Bike Light
Remove Sauce Labs Onesie, continue shopping, and re-add the product
Proceed from the Products page to the Checkout page
Verify total price and finalize the order
